</h2>				
					<h3>1. Terms &amp; Conditions of Use
</h3>				
		<p>By accessing this website, you agree to these Terms and Conditions of Use, as updated by Stairway Mortgage, a Division of NEXA Mortgage LLC (“Stairway Mortgage”). If you do not accept these terms, please discontinue use immediately.</p><p><b>Eligibility:</b> You must be at least 18 years old and a U.S. resident to use this website or any services provided.</p><ol start="2"><li><b>Limited Use License</b><b><br /></b>You are granted a limited, non-transferable license to use this website solely for mortgage-related services.<br />Unauthorized copying, reselling, or redistribution of website content is strictly prohibited.</li><li><b>Proprietary Rights</b><b><br /></b>All website content—including text, images, data, software, and trademarks—is protected under U.S. and international copyright laws.<br />Your use of this website does not transfer ownership rights of any intellectual property belonging to Stairway Mortgage.</li><li><b>Disclaimers</b><b><br /></b>This website is provided “as is” without warranties of any kind. Stairway Mortgage makes no guarantees regarding:</li></ol><ul><li>The accuracy or reliability of content.</li><li>The availability or uninterrupted operation of the website.</li><li>The website’s ability to meet your specific needs.</li></ul><p>Use of this site is at your own risk.</p><ol start="5"><li><b>Limitation of Liability</b><b><br /></b>Stairway Mortgage is not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages resulting from your use of this website.<br />Your sole remedy is to discontinue use of the website.</li><li><b>Jurisdiction &amp; Legal Venue</b><b><br /></b>These terms are governed by U.S. law.<br />Any legal disputes must be resolved in the state or federal courts where Stairway Mortgage’s principal office is located.</li><li><b>Indemnification</b><b><br /></b>You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Stairway Mortgage, its affiliates, officers, employees, and agents from any claims, liabilities, or legal fees arising from:</li></ol><ul><li>Your use of the website.</li><li>Any violation of these Terms.</li><li>Infringement of third-party rights.</li></ul><ol start="8"><li><b>COPPA Compliance</b><b><br /></b>This website is not intended for individuals under 18.<br />Parents can use filtering software to restrict access.<br />See our Privacy Policy for details on data protection.</li><li><b>Technology Export Control</b><b><br /></b>Users must comply with U.S. export laws and not transmit restricted software or technology to unauthorized individuals or foreign entities.</li><li><b>Service Changes &amp; Interruptions</b><b><br /></b>Stairway Mortgage reserves the right to:</li></ol><ul><li>Modify, suspend, or discontinue the website or services at any time without notice.</li><li>Not be held responsible for service interruptions.</li></ul><ol start="11"><li><b>Third-Party Links</b><b><br /></b>This website may include links to third-party sites for convenience.<br />Stairway Mortgage does not endorse or take responsibility for their content or policies.<br />Access third-party sites at your own risk.</li><li><b>Copyright Infringement Claims</b><b><br /></b>If you believe your copyrighted material has been used without permission, submit a detailed notice to:</li></ol><p><b>Legal Department – Stairway Mortgage, a Division of NEXA Mortgage LLC</b><b><br /></b>3100 W Ray Road #201, Office #209, Chandler, AZ 85226<br />info@nexamortgage.com<br />(602) 344-9333</p><p>Your claim must include:</p><ul><li>Your name &amp; contact details.</li><li>A sworn statement that you own the copyright or are authorized to act on behalf of the copyright owner.</li></ul><p><b>Product-Specific Disclosures</b></p><ul><li><b>FHA, VA, &amp; USDA Loans:</b> Subject to underwriting approval and specific program restrictions. Contact us for details.</li><li><b>Reverse Mortgages:</b> Require approved counseling. Homeowners remain responsible for taxes &amp; insurance.</li><li><b>HELOC Products:</b> Failure to repay may result in foreclosure.</li></ul><p><b>Vulnerability Disclosure Policy</b><b><br /></b>We prioritize security and employ protections like encryption and firewalls.<br />To report security vulnerabilities, email <b>info@nexamortgage.com</b> with “Vulnerability Disclosure” in the subject line.</p><p><b>Compliance with State-Specific Notices</b><b><br /></b><b>Texas Residents:</b> Consumers can file complaints with the Texas Department of Savings and Mortgage Lending at:<br />2601 N. Lamar, Suite 201, Austin, TX 78705<br />Visit<a href="http://www.sml.texas.gov/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"> <b>www.sml.texas.gov</b></a></p><p><b>Equal Housing Opportunity</b><b><br /></b>Stairway Mortgage is an Equal Housing Lender and complies with federal laws prohibiting discrimination based on:</p><ul><li>Race, color, religion, national origin, sex, marital status, age</li><li>Public assistance income sources</li><li>Consumer Credit Protection Act rights</li></ul><p><b>Disclaimer:</b> Loan programs may change without notice. Borrowers must meet program eligibility requirements.</p>		
					<h3>“Refi 36” Terms and Conditions
</h3>				
		<h3><b>Offer to Refinance Once Within 36 Months of Closing Date</b></h3><h3><b>1. Offer Overview</b></h3><p>Stairway Mortgage (“Stairway”) offers qualified customers up to <b>\$2,500 in lender-paid credits</b> when refinancing a <b>first-lien purchase or refinance mortgage loan</b> (“Mortgage Loan”) with Stairway within <b>36 months</b> of the original closing date.</p><p><b>Eligibility begins after 180 days</b> from the original funding date.<br /><b>Note:</b> This offer is valid only through a <b>Stairway Mortgage branch of NEXA Mortgage LLC</b> and <b>cannot be redeemed through any other NEXA Mortgage branch, team, or affiliate</b>.</p><h3>2. Covered Fees</h3><p>Lender credits may be applied toward the following eligible fees:</p><h4><b>Included Fees:</b></h4><ul><li>Lender’s &amp; Owner’s Title Insurance</li><li>Appraisal (including second appraisal, re-inspection, and recertification)</li><li>Flood Certification</li><li>Credit Report</li><li>Settlement Fees (including notary, recording, transfer taxes, government fees, deed preparation, courier, and endorsements)</li></ul><h4><b>Excluded Fees:</b></h4><ul><li>Discount Points</li><li>Any cash back to the borrower</li></ul><h3>3. Eligibility Requirements</h3><p>To qualify for the “Refi 36” offer, customers must:</p><ul><li>Be a <b>U.S. citizen</b>, <b>permanent resident</b>, or <b>eligible non-permanent resident</b> refinancing a <b>primary residence</b> in a state where Stairway is licensed.</li><li>Have closed their Mortgage Loan with Stairway between <b>January 1, 2025, and December 31, 2030</b>.</li><li>Refinance their Mortgage Loan with Stairway within <b>36 months</b> of the original closing date.</li><li>Notify their Loan Consultant <b>before locking</b> their refinance rate.</li></ul><h3>4. Additional Terms</h3><ul><li><b>One-Time Use:</b> Offer is limited to <b>one refinance transaction</b> and may not be combined with other promotions.</li><li><b>No Cash Value:</b> Credits apply only toward Covered Fees and <b>cannot be exchanged for cash</b> or exceed actual costs.</li><li><b>Subject to Approval:</b> All applications require standard <b>underwriting and credit approval</b>.</li></ul><h3>5. Equal Housing and Compliance</h3><p>Stairway Mortgage complies with all applicable <b>federal fair lending laws</b> and does not discriminate based on race, color, religion, national origin, sex, marital status, age, source of income, or rights under the <b>Consumer Credit Protection Act</b>.</p><p>Oversight by the <b>Federal Trade Commission (FTC), Washington, DC, 20580</b>.<br /><b>Disclosure:</b> This is <b>not a commitment to lend</b>. Please contact us for full details.</p><h3>6. Policy Changes</h3><p>Stairway Mortgage reserves the right to <b>modify or discontinue</b> this offer, promotions, or benefits at any time without prior notice. Rates, terms, and eligibility are subject to change and may vary by state.</p><h3>Corporate Contact Information</h3><p><b>Corporate Address</b><b><br /></b><b>Stairway Mortgage, a Division of <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/nexa-mortgage-partnership/"  data-wpil-monitor-id="308">NEXA Mortgage</a> LLC</b></p><p>5559 S Sossaman Rd, Bldg 1 Ste 101 Mesa, AZ 85212</p><p>(602) 344-9333<br />info@nexamortgage.com</p>`} />
